  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Field Engineer(Construction)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Our Company:</strong></h3>\n<p>Our company develops ICT(Information and Communication Technology) solutions for domestic and foreign customers to solve their problems pertaining to construction and civil engineering.</p>\n<p>The shield excavation management system and automatic survey system developed by our company are used at tunnel construction sites in Japan and overseas.</p>\n<p><em>https://www.enzan-k.com/eng/index.html</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Roles and Job Responsibilities :</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>To travel to customers sites for support, troubleshoot and maintain software Field / Site.</li>\n  <li>To support commissioning and decommissioning on CCTV/software</li>\n  <li>To generate service report post, service support and projects.</li>\n  <li>To support other ad-hoc duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidate possess Diploma in Engineering (Electrical/Electronic)/IT, Civil Engineering or equivalent.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Preferably 1 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Able to complete task with little or no supervision.</p>\n<p>Positive attitude.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Motivated Team player.</p>",
